title: Pond- Discography (2009-2015) 6 Albums
description:
Pond is a psychedelic rock band from Perth, Western Australia which formed in 2008. Featuring an ever-changing line-up, the current line up is Nick Allbrook, Jay Watson, Joseph Ryan, Jamie Terry, Cam Avery and Matt Handley. After the success of Tame Impala's 2010 breakthrough debut album Innerspeaker, a band which shares three members with Pond, the album Beard, Wives, Denim was recorded in 2010 and later released to critical acclaim in March 2012.


Albums:


Psychedelic Mango (9 January 2009)
Corridors of Blissterday (4 June 2009)
Frond (24 May 2010)
Beard, Wives, Denim (2 March 2012) 
Hobo Rocket (2 August 2013)
Man It Feels Like Space Again (2015)
